I gotta disagree.  Ok lvl 34 Mid Sun is chained off a block style (Valk Shield) so its not so good.  However, Glacial Movement as a side positional is decent (39 spec).  Arctic Rift (44 spec) as a follow-up to Evernight rear positional is great.  Its high damage and low endurance and used for all the silly people who try to run from skalds.<br>
